"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/60970","Department for Work and Pensions","false","2014-06-17","<p /> <p /> <p>The information requested is published and can be found at:</p><p> </p><p><a href="http://tabulation-tool.dwp.gov.uk/WorkProg/tabtool.html" target="_blank">http://tabulation-tool.dwp.gov.uk/WorkProg/tabtool.html</a></p><p> </p><p>Guidance for users is available at:</p><p> </p><p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/dwp-tabulation-tool-guidance" target="_blank">https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/dwp-tabulation-tool-guidance</a></p>","Wirral West","Esther McVey",,"2014-06-17T14:32:35.5284993Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/60970/answer","Biography information for Esther McVey","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/60970/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/60970/answer",,,,,,,,,"29","Work and Pensions","Work and Pensions","2014-06-10","Work Programme: North East","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Work and Pensions, how many people resident in (a) Washington and Sunderland West constituency, (b) the Sunderland local authority area and (c) the North East region have been referred to the work programme to date; and how many of those have achieved sustained job outcomes.","false","Biography information for Mrs Sharon Hodgson","Washington and Sunderland West","Mrs Sharon Hodgson","199858"
